X7 통산경력
team 구단명
player 선수명

연습문제 6.12 (수정)

regselectsim <- function(selmethod) {

    set.seed(13221)

    Nsim <- 10
    variables.set <- NULL
    r2.set <- NULL
    r2adj.set <- NULL
    p <- NULL

    for (i in 1:Nsim) {

        randata <- matrix(rnorm(5100), ncol = 51)
        randata <- data.frame(randata)

        if (selmethod == "F-BACK") {

            fit.lm <- lm(X1 ~ ., data = randata)
            res <- step(fit.lm, test = "F", drection = "backward", trace = 0)

            variable.entered <- as.character(attr(res$terms, "variables"))[-(1:2)]
            variables.set <- c(variables.set, variable.entered)
            p <- c(p, length(variable.entered))
            r2.set <- c(r2.set, summary(res)$r.squared)
            r2adj.set <- c(r2adj.set, summary(res)$adj.r.squared)

        } else if (selmethod == "AIC-BACK") {

            fit.lm <- lm(X1 ~ ., data = randata)
            res <- step(fit.lm, drection = "backward", trace = 0)

            variable.entered <- as.character(attr(res$terms, "variables"))[-(1:2)]
            variables.set <- c(variables.set, variable.entered)
            p <- c(p, length(variable.entered))
            r2.set <- c(r2.set, summary(res)$r.squared)
            r2adj.set <- c(r2adj.set, summary(res)$adj.r.squared)
        } else if (selmethod == "F-FORW") {

            fit.null <- lm(X1 ~ 1, data = randata)
            res <- step(fit.null, scope ~ X2 + X3 + X4 + X5 + X6 + X7 + X8 + X9 + X10 + X11 + 
                X12 + X13 + X14 + X15 + X16 + X17 + X18 + X19 + X20 + X21 + X22 + X23 + X24 + 
                X25 + X26 + X27 + X28 + X29 + X30 + X31 + X32 + X33 + X34 + X35 + X36 + X37 + 
                X38 + X39 + X40 + X41 + X42 + X43 + X44 + X45 + X46 + X47 + X48 + X49 + X50 + 
                X51, test = "F", direction = "forward", trace = 0)

            variable.entered <- as.character(attr(res$terms, "variables"))[-(1:2)]
            variables.set <- c(variables.set, variable.entered)
            p <- c(p, length(variable.entered))
            r2.set <- c(r2.set, summary(res)$r.squared)
            r2adj.set <- c(r2adj.set, summary(res)$adj.r.squared)
        } else if (selmethod == "AIC-FORW") {

            fit.null <- lm(X1 ~ 1, data = randata)
            res <- step(fit.null, scope ~ X2 + X3 + X4 + X5 + X6 + X7 + X8 + X9 + X10 + X11 + 
                X12 + X13 + X14 + X15 + X16 + X17 + X18 + X19 + X20 + X21 + X22 + X23 + X24 + 
                X25 + X26 + X27 + X28 + X29 + X30 + X31 + X32 + X33 + X34 + X35 + X36 + X37 + 
                X38 + X39 + X40 + X41 + X42 + X43 + X44 + X45 + X46 + X47 + X48 + X49 + X50 + 
                X51, direction = "forward", trace = 0)

            variable.entered <- as.character(attr(res$terms, "variables"))[-(1:2)]
            variables.set <- c(variables.set, variable.entered)
            p <- c(p, length(variable.entered))
            r2.set <- c(r2.set, summary(res)$r.squared)
            r2adj.set <- c(r2adj.set, summary(res)$adj.r.squared)
        }

    }

    list(varset = variables.set, varlength = p, r2 = r2.set, r2adj = r2adj.set)

}
